      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "# *Developing a function for the RDecesion Treet Algorithm and applying dataset to this model*"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "8r5gZXDtZZB4"
      },
      "id": "8r5gZXDtZZB4"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Importing Libraries"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "HCnseHeTZ6Xo"
      },
      "id": "HCnseHeTZ6Xo"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "2ca23bff"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n",
        "import time"
      ],
      "id": "2ca23bff"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Mounting Google Drive to access the dataset"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "wWDLc438ZYT8"
      },
      "id": "wWDLc438ZYT8"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "c_e_k5kAkLP7",
        "outputId": "8c670b87-4d4d-47d9-9c9f-765a07298059"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Mounted at /content/drive\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "from google.colab import drive\n",
        "drive.mount('/content/drive')"
      ],
      "id": "c_e_k5kAkLP7"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "1c5c1eb0"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# Reading data from csv file\n",
        "dataset = pd.read_csv('/content/drive/MyDrive/ML_2023/processed_dataset.csv')\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "id": "1c5c1eb0"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Creating a function to buld and train the ML Model"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "iDqmp6pqiQ2Q"
      },
      "id": "iDqmp6pqiQ2Q"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "x = pd.DataFrame(dataset.iloc[:, 0:4].values)\n",
        "y = dataset.iloc[:, 4].values"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "smbqqLMjiR7v"
      },
      "id": "smbqqLMjiR7v",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "85084dd8"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "#Generating training and test data sets\n",
        "x_train, x_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(x, y, test_size = 0.3, random_state = 123)"
      ],
      "id": "85084dd8"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "b2b5b7d4",
        "outputId": "c84028eb-2124-41b0-fa68-0ab5fdf1c14e"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Fit Time: 0.35364184379577637 seconds\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "# Importing Decesion Tree\n",
        "from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeRegressor\n",
        "\n",
        "DTReg = DecisionTreeRegressor()\n",
        "start_time = time.time()\n",
        "DTReg.fit(x_train,y_train)\n",
        "end_time = time.time()\n",
        "fit_time = end_time - start_time\n",
        "print(\"Fit Time:\", fit_time, \"seconds\")"
      ],
      "id": "b2b5b7d4"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "154dcf05"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "start_time = time.time()\n",
        "y_pred = DTReg.predict(x_test)\n",
        "end_time = time.time()\n",
        "prediction_time = end_time - start_time"
      ],
      "id": "154dcf05"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "9abb735e",
        "outputId": "3222fa9c-1fd9-47b2-a393-49bb83cd4dae"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Mean Squared Error 6.257210019915039\n",
            "R-Squared:  0.7154002209175563\n",
            "Max Error 31.588399219999996\n",
            "Mean Absolute Error 0.9873467672549709\n",
            "MAPE 0.1045408851312994\n",
            "Prediction Time: 0.009168786048916016 seconds\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "# Prediction Metrics\n",
        "\n",
        "from sklearn.metrics import r2_score\n",
        "from sklearn.metrics import mean_squared_error as mse\n",
        "from sklearn.metrics import max_error\n",
        "from sklearn.metrics import mean_absolute_error\n",
        "from sklearn.metrics import mean_absolute_percentage_error\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "MSE = mse(y_test, y_pred)\n",
        "R2 = r2_score(y_test, y_pred)\n",
        "MAX_ERROR = max_error(y_test, y_pred);\n",
        "MEAN_ABSOLUTE_ERROR = mean_absolute_error(y_test, y_pred)\n",
        "MAPE = mean_absolute_percentage_error(y_test, y_pred)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Mean Squared Error\", MSE)\n",
        "print(\"R-Squared: \", R2)\n",
        "print(\"Max Error\", MAX_ERROR);\n",
        "print(\"Mean Absolute Error\", MEAN_ABSOLUTE_ERROR);\n",
        "print(\"MAPE\", MAPE);\n",
        "print(\"Prediction Time:\", prediction_time, \"seconds\")"
      ],
      "id": "9abb735e"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Create a function that will plot a graph between the predicted and actual values"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "jtJy1o5PjlRv"
      },
      "id": "jtJy1o5PjlRv"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "plt.scatter(x=y_test, y=y_pred, c='crimson', alpha=0.6)\n",
        "plt.plot(y_pred, y_pred,color='black', linestyle='dashed')\n",
        "plt.title('Actual vs. Predicted Values of Return Loss (Decesion Tree)')\n",
        "plt.xlabel('Actual values (dB)')\n",
        "plt.ylabel('Predicted values (dB)')\n",
        "plt.show()"
